-1.title: Electric Jump
-1.plot: Jumping from a moving car; drag race between electric and traditional car; Vanessa and Garrett slam into roadside targets.

1.title: Ripping Off the Roof
1.plot: Vanessa tackles a stunt that scares even industry veterans - the fearsome 50mph can opener! The team explode some myths about how Hollywood blows a car apart without a real bomb, they push rubber to the limit with a challenge to see just how fast they can blow a car's tires, and Garrett risks life and limb testing the theory that a car can protect you from a deadly lightning strike.

2.title: Bulletproof Beater
2.plot: In this episode of Stuntbusters, Garrett and Vanessa break out the big guns to find out how you can shoot out the tires on a speeding getaway car. They put torque to the test with the ultimate truck tug of war to see which emerges victorious. Car windshie

3.title: Ultimate Flip
3.plot: Garrett and Vanessa put a new spin on a gravity defying cable assisted car flip stunt.

4.title: Big Guns
4.plot: In this episode of Stuntbusters, Garrett and Vanessa break out the big guns to find out how you can shoot out the tires on a speeding getaway car. They put torque to the test with the ultimate truck tug of war to see which emerges victorious. Car Windshields are put to the test with a high impact projectile test, and and old car is slammed head on into a new model to see which one survives.

5.title: Car Hit Meltdown
5.plot: In the episode the Stuntbusters demonstrate how Hollywood stages a realistic car hit without killing the stuntman. Vanessa gets a crash course in driving a monster truck and quickly takes on a massive jump.

6.title: Wall of Fire
6.plot: Garrett rides the hood of a car in a fire stunt; how to stage a motorcycle crash; Vanessa gets more muscle from a V8; 250 feet of detonator cord plus an SUV equals...? Only on SPEED.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Vanessa and Garrett attempt to "drift" a semi truck; Garrett escapes a sinking car; using specials effects to create an explosion.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Garrett crashes a sidewinder; the secrets behind a realistic RPG explosion; Vanessa gets pointers on driving formula cars; an SUV collides with a compact car.

9.title: 180 on 18
9.plot: Stuntbusters makes driving history by doing a 180 in an 18 wheeler; Vanessa drives a car off a ramp; Man versus Machine in the ultimate parking challenge.

10.title: Slide, Drag, Launch
10.plot: Vanessa slides through a deadly wall of fire. Garrett transforms a jeep into a sleek aerodynamic car. The Stuntbusters demonstrate the most challenging motorcycle stunt...the highside. And what happens when you launch a car off a cliff.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: A car "skis" on two wheels; testing a vehicle's load-bearing capacity; a muddy road test; special effects teams blows a car into the air. Only on SPEED

13.title: Bringing Down the House
13.plot: Sending a car through a flaming house; car rollovers and rear end collisions; propelling a car with an explosive air cannon.

imdb.plot outline: Stuntbusters is going to explore and explode motoring myths as we reveal the facts and figures behind the latest, fastest and hottest automotive technology on earth! Join our two fearless human crash test dummy stunt drivers as they take it to the redline and beyond using our high-tech test lab equipped with cutting edge automotive technology and eye-popping graphic interfaces. Each high-octane experiment will be captured at one thousand frames per second; allowing us to slow the action down and dive into the physics behind the vehicular carnage! Only on SPEED.
